snippet.title: So Who Is Dr Rabbit CD ROM 1997
snippet.description: Featuring the original voice of Dr Rabbit Marty Nelson. I recorded the interactive book as well as some of the scenes where Dr Rabbit comes in and I also added a few of the MOV files he's in at the end.
